#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:1 of
msgid ""
"Generate text using a text language model based on given data and prompt "
"template."
msgstr "使用指定的文本语言模型，基于给定的数据和提示模板生成文本。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:3 of
msgid ""
"Input data used for generation. Can be maxframe DataFrame, Series that "
"contain text to be processed."
msgstr "用于生成的输入数据。可以是包含待处理文本的 maxframe DataFrame、Series。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:5 of
msgid "Language model instance used for text generation."
msgstr "用于文本生成的语言模型实例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dictionary containing the conversation messages template. Use "
"``{col_name}`` as a placeholder to reference column data from input data."
"  Usually in format of [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{query}\"}], "
"same with openai api schema."
msgstr ""
"包含对话消息模板的字典。使用 ``{col_name}`` 作为占位符来引用输入数据中的"
"列数据。通常格式为 [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{query}\"}]，与 "
"openai api 模式一致。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dictionary containing the conversation messages template. Use "
"``{col_name}`` as a placeholder to reference column data from input data."
msgstr ""
"包含对话消息模板的字典。使用 ``{col_name}`` 作为占位符来引用输入数据中的"
"列数据。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:10 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Usually in format of [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{query}\"}], "
"same with openai api schema."
msgstr ""
"通常格式为 [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{query}\"}]，与 openai "
"api 模式一致。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:12 of
msgid ""
"Additional parameters for generation configuration, by default None. Can "
"include settings like temperature, max_tokens, etc."
msgstr ""
"用于生成配置的附加参数，默认为 None。可以包括 temperature、max_tokens 等"
"设置。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.text.generate:16 of
msgid ""
"Generated text raw response and success status. If the success is False, "
"the generated text will return the error message."
msgstr ""
"生成文本的原始响应和成功状态。如果成功状态为 False，则生成的文本将返回"
"错误信息。"

